data.description: **Move in Ready** Are you ready to embark on an exciting journey to find your very first family home or craving a refreshing change? Immerse yourself in the cozy embrace of this enchanting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven, complete with an extra den to cater to your expanding needs. As you explore this charming neighborhood, picture yourself leisurely strolling towards the inviting Bethel pool, just a stone's throw away, promising endless relaxation and enjoyment. Your dream home adventure awaits!  Interested in Hobgood School, there is a bus stop for Hobgood near DANITE Restaurant in Bethel.
